data.description: Welcome to this charming ranch-style home! With its spacious deck and cozy backyard, this property offers the perfect retreat for relaxation and entertainment. Boasting two bedrooms and two full baths, it provides ample space for comfortable living. The fully finished basement adds extra versatility, offering additional room for recreation or storage. Conveniently, the two-car garage provides ample parking and storage options. Don't miss the opportunity to make this inviting ranch-style home your own!
